---
title: Quick Double Southern Cheesy Pork & Veggie Quesadillas with Garlic Aioli
description: Juicy Southern-spiced pork, garlic aioli and melted Cheddar cheese; it’s hard to resist these incredibly delicious quesadillas.
Plus, spices and aromas will have everyone ready at the table to dig into this fun feast!
